                    <enum>(1)</enum>
                    <header display-inline="yes-display-inline">In general</header>
 <text>Section 322(a) of the Energy Policy and Conservation Act (<external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/42/6292">42 U.S.C. 6292(a)</external-xref>) is amended—</text>
                    <subparagraph id="idd397d3eb2edf449483f424c52812220a" commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline">
                        <enum>(A)</enum>
 <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">by striking paragraph (14); and</text>
