                        <enum>(B)</enum>
 <text>by redesignating paragraphs (15) through (20) as paragraphs (14) through (19), respectively.</text>
                    </subparagraph>
                </paragraph>
                <paragraph id="idfb784ac115d84c5e81e19b215ab069b3">
