                    </subparagraph>
                    <subparagraph id="id45345d73cca243a8a3c91ed8b6717ac9">
                        <enum>(B)</enum>
 <text>Section 324 of the Energy Policy and Conservation Act (<external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/42/6294">42 U.S.C. 6294</external-xref>) is amended—</text>
