 <text>Section 325(n)(1) of the Energy Policy and Conservation Act (<external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/42/6295">42 U.S.C. 6295(n)(1)</external-xref>) is amended by striking <quote>(11), and in paragraphs (13) and (14)</quote> and inserting <quote>(11) and (13)</quote>.</text>
