 <text>The rule of the Department of Energy entitled <quote>Energy Conservation Program: Definitions for General Service Lamps</quote> (87 Fed. Reg. 27461 (May 9, 2022)).</text>
                </paragraph>
                <paragraph commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="id1d853c5b56844368b3c1bf2ac2839323">
